title: Jennifer Dlouhy on Paris Agreement (Audio)
itunes:title: Jennifer Dlouhy on Paris Agreement (Audio)
description:
(Bloomberg) -- Jennifer Dlouhy, a Bloomberg News Reporter, will discuss what the U.S role could be in the Paris climate accord. She speaks with Michael Best and Greg Stohr on "Bloomberg Law."
